required libraries
===================
numpy
scipy
sklearn


training_file format
=====================
as given inside the directory 'Data'

others
=======
must need to create a empty directory named 'Models'

folder structure
=================

--tamilParaPhrase
	-- Code
		-- classifier.py
		-- config.py
		-- featurizer.py
		-- load_data.py
		-- paraPhrase_test.py
		-- paraPhrase_train.py
		-- representation.py
	-- Data
		-- testing_labels.txt
		-- test_pairs.txt
		-- training_labels.txt
		-- train_pairs.txt
	-- Models
	-- Readme

2. change the parameters in "config.py" in the folder "code"





Testing:

1. service.py - It serves light weight bottle based python service at port 8000  (http://localhost:8000), can be easilly configured.

2. model - model will be selected as algorithm choosed in "config.py" file


